{"tid":2232503,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陳同佳案｜地檢署稱未接投案消息 台律師：潘媽媽求情都要坐5至10年","createTime":"2020-10-06T12:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T13:45:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"a0a677da9ec45ef34ba98629737186347085e933","tid":2232503,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:05:45.000Z","msg":"（更新：內容）涉嫌於2018年台灣殺死女友潘曉穎的香港男子陳同佳，去年刑滿出獄後揚言到台灣投案，牽動兩岸三地敏感神經，上周他又透露計劃本月來台，並透過香港聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴牧師表示已委託台灣律師昨天會晤台灣當局。對此，理律法律事務所昨晚雖首度證實由凃榆政律師接受陳同佳委任，但承辦陳同佳案的士林地檢署至今仍未接獲相關訊息。<br />\n<br />\n士林地檢署指出，今天至中午為止，都沒有陳同佳案相關的消息與進展。本報記者中午致電理律事務所，欲聯絡凃律師了解情況，但接聽女職員表示他不在辦公室。記者已透過電郵向凃律師作出查詢，惟至今未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201006/CXAV3DMSQVCF5GD32FOQV6S544/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201006%2FCXAV3DMSQVCF5GD32FOQV6S544%2F&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKGWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=ba6420e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201006%2FCXAV3DMSQVCF5GD32FOQV6S544%2F&h=7966fd52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201006/CXAV3DMSQVCF5GD32FOQV6S544/</a>"},{"pid":"ad38900c13bf7b3e03f07b1c71c9e402d3645a3a","tid":2232503,"uid":286897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:07:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"497aa2cfd46ed79765cdc1bb7ddbe2f12dd83287","tid":2232503,"uid":151313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"死者老母仲要幫兇手求情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9d83584b426cf6a63d5c6501c179e317c0247c","tid":2232503,"uid":70771,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:09:12.000Z","msg":"邊有可能殺左人淨係坐5-10年啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a50a9ca4752784d35066d7d091f3e61f5a994a","tid":2232503,"uid":106320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb9d83584b426cf6a63d